       Megatron takes the disk from Scorpinox. "What is this now?"

       Ominous and the other five Energonians make themselfs comfortable. 
They returned to the Orb to think of another plan. 
       "Whatever happened with Zardus commander? Will he help us or is going 
to have to be destroyed as well?" Putnam asked.
       Ominous didnt know what he was going to do about Zardus, he seemed to 
be very manipulative. If Ominous didnt take advantage of him, then Zardus was 
going to take advantage of Ominous. "Get him on the comm....we have 
arrangements to make. With or without him."

--part1_a9.10ea361a.27a427e6_boundary
